{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "不带刀的叶开从荒原长街走入一处奇怪场所，立刻注意到黑衣持刀的傅红雪。叶开以邀酒挑起交谈，又戏弄紫衫佩剑少年，弹断其剑，并用金豆请满屋人喝酒。傅红雪冷淡离去后，万马堂白衣人奉三老板之命相邀，却被他置之不理，只能守在街心。夜里傅红雪进入黑暗小屋，与久候的神秘少女相会；清晨又向老太婆预付房钱和棺材钱。白日长街上万马堂骑士飞驰立旗，关东万马堂的声威正式压到傅红雪面前。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像我这种人的脚，怎么也和别人的脚一样会破呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你这么不中用，我就叫你再多受些折磨，多受些苦。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你从来不喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你不喝，请我喝两杯怎么样？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你要我请你喝酒？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "为什么？因为我觉得你很顺眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这地方除了你之外，简直连一个顺眼的人都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你肯不肯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这是你最好的机会了，你若错过，岂非很可惜？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不可惜。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你这人果然有趣，老实说，除了你之外，别人就算跪下来求我，我也不会喝他一滴酒的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我请你喝杯酒好不好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你要怎么样才肯喝？跪下来求你好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "只不过你就算跪下来，我还是不喝的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "不清楚，我连你究竟是不是个人，都不太清楚。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你看，我没有骗你吧，别人想请我喝酒都困难得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你没有骗我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你请不请呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "你应该用买衣服的钱，去买把好剑的；但最好还是从此不要佩剑，用剑来做装饰，实在危险得很。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁观者",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "原来他是个跛子。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_li_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "华丽中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不愿别人请你喝酒，愿不愿意请别人喝酒呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_hua_li_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "别人请我是一回事，我请不请别人，又是另外一回事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_li_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "华丽中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不错，那完全不同的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我请，这屋子里每个人我都请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过我请人喝酒的时候，谁不喝都不行，不喝醉也不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道请人喝酒要银子的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "银子？你看我身上像不像带着银子的人？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的确不像。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "幸好买酒并不一定要用银子的，用豆子也行。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "豆子？什么豆子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "就是这种豆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只有一样事不懂。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "你不懂的事，我一定懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不要别人请你喝酒，为什么要请别人，那又有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "若有条狗要请你去吃屎，你吃不吃？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衫少年",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当然不吃。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_zi_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "我也不吃的，但我却时常喂狗。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "阁下请留步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "恕在下冒昧请教，不知阁下是不是今天才到这里的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "阁下从哪里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "阁下是否很快就要走呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "也许。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "也许不走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "也许。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "阁下暂时若不走，三老板就想请阁下明夜移驾过去一叙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "三老板？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "在下说的，当然就是'万马堂'的三老板。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "三老板吩咐在下，务必要请阁下赏光，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "否则怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "否则在下回去也无法交待，就只有站在这里不走了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "就站在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "站到几时？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "站到阁下肯答应为止。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "很好……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ti_deng_long_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "提灯笼的人",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "就这样放他走？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我已等了很久。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "你的确等了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你是什么时候来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "今天，黄昏。",
